
1. References
 - https://bitbucket.org/tildeslash/monit/
 
2. Pre-requisites
 - CentOS 7.x
 
3. Installation
 - curl -LO# ...
 - tar xvzf ...
 - cd ...
 - ./bootstrap
 - ./configure
 - make
 - make install
  
4. Post-installation
 - check service page
  + access http://127.0.0.1:2812 on the browser with account admin/monit
  